  "decision_conditions": [
    "Reason : 1 - Under Schedule 2, Part 3, Class MA of the General Permitted Development Order 2015 (as amended), prior approval would be required and REFUSED for the following reason: \r\n\r\nIn the absence of adequate secure and accessible cycle storage facilities for the development, the scheme fails to promote a sustainable form of development contrary to Policy T5 of the London Plan 2021 and Merton Core Strategy 2011 policy CS18. \r\n\r\n\r\n",
    "Reason : 2 - Under Schedule 2, Part 3, Class MA of the General Permitted Development Order 2015 (as amended), prior approval would be required and REFUSED for the following reason: \r\n\r\nIn the absence of adequate refuse storage facilities for the development, the scheme would adversely impact on the free flow of traffic and pedestrian and vehicular safety on the surrounding roads.  The scheme fails to comply with, in particular, Policy T6 of the London Plan and Policy CS.19 of the Merton Core Planning Strategy 2011. \r\n\r\n\r\n",
    "Reason : 3 - Under Schedule 2, Part 3, Class MA of the General Permitted Development Order 2015 (as amended), prior approval would be required and REFUSED for the following reason: \r\n\r\nBy reason of the unacceptable layout the scheme represents over-intensification and over-development of the site that would result in sub-standard living conditions and environment, to the detriment of the amenities of future occupiers.  The development would thereby be contrary to, in particular, policy DM D2 of Merton Sites and Policies Plan (2014), policy D6 of the London Plan 2021, the Technical Housing Standards - Nationally Described Space Standard (March 2015) and fail to comply with Article 3, Paragraph 9A of the Town and Country Planning (General Permitted Development) Order 2015 (as amended).\r\n"
  ],
